OL,3,CBuilding crumbles to the ground after
OL,4,Cmajor crash during police chase
OL,6,FA driver has ploughed into a takeaway
OL,7,Fas they were being chased by police,
OL,8,Fbefore the building dramatically
OL,9,Fcollapsed in Heywood.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police said that
OL,12,Fofficers had originally been called
OL,13,Fout to a disturbance at a house in
OL,14,FBury.
OL,16,FA man left the scene in a car, and
OL,17,Fpolice began to pursue it.
OL,19,FAs the vehicle left Bury and drove
OL,20,Fthrough Heywood, it crashed into the
OL,21,Ffront of the building.
