OL,3,CBuilding crumbles to the ground after
OL,4,Cmajor crash during police chase
OL,6,FIt is believed that the damaged
OL,7,Fbuilding is the Heywood Star takeaway.
OL,9,FThe force said a man in his 30s has
OL,10,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of failing
OL,11,Fto stop, dangerous driving and threats
OL,12,Fto kill.
OL,14,FHe was then taken to hospital for
OL,15,Ftreatment.
OL,17,FA GMP spokesperson said: "At around
OL,18,F3.50am this morning (Sunday 28
OL,19,FSeptember 2025), we responded to
OL,20,Freports of an ongoing disturbance at
OL,21,Fan address on Walmersley Road in Bury.
