OL,6,F"Upon police arrival a vehicle made
OL,7,Foff resulting in a pursuit utilising
OL,8,Fspecialist tactics.
OL,10,F"Investigations are ongoing. Officers
OL,11,Fare now appealing for anyone who
OL,12,Fwitnessed the incident to come forward
OL,13,Fand assist their investigation."
OL,15,FBridge Street remains closed off this
OL,16,Fafternoon, with a silver car seen
OL,17,Fcrushed under bricks and debris.
OL,19,FCouncil officials are at the scene,
OL,20,Fwith an investigation concerning the
OL,21,Fsafety of the building ongoing.
