OL,3,CBuilding crumbles to the ground after
OL,4,Cmajor crash during police chase
OL,6,FA pile of rubble can be on the ground,
OL,7,Fincluding a sign reading 'Heywood
OL,8,FStar'.
OL,10,FThe front wall of the building was
OL,11,Ftorn off, with the first floor also
OL,12,Fexposed and shelves seen hanging off
OL,13,Fthe edge.
OL,15,FCouncil officials moved people away
OL,16,Ffrom the scene due to fears the
OL,17,Fstructure was unstable.
