OL,3,CBuilding crumbles to the ground after
OL,4,Cmajor crash during police chase
OL,6,FDiggers were later drafted in as part
OL,7,Fof the major clean up operation, with
OL,8,Fa crowd of onlookers watching from the
OL,9,Fedge of the cordon.
OL,11,FPictures show a heap of bricks and
OL,12,Fdebris on the ground, with the inside
OL,13,Fof the building exposed.
OL,15,FOne person claimed a car had been
OL,16,Fspeeding in the area moments before
OL,17,Fthe crash, which saw a vehicle plough
OL,18,Finto the front of a building: "The
OL,19,Fnoise I heard at 4.40am was no doubt
OL,20,Fgoing to end badly," one person said.
